{"tid":1069903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園出post致敬《春光乍洩》 網民盼有女女版","createTime":"2019-03-20T09:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T11:29:21.000Z","uid":148,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"972d619ec20180c9501c5ef66e2d6d7728e0dcce","tid":1069903,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190320/large/1553066736_9538.png \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190320%2Flarge%2F1553066736_9538.png%20&h=ca56e64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海洋公園近日出咗個post（右圖），引起網民瘋傳。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣近年嘅同志平權運動取得突破，行政院通過同性伴侶可以《民法》婚姻章規定結婚，而且享有法定權利，仲喺今年5月尾生效。唔知係咪呢個原因，香港海洋公園facebook嘅台灣版面，近日就出咗個post ，仲俾網民瘋狂share。<br />\n<br />\n「我想你陪我一下，我好想你陪我一下。」相信睇過金馬獎得獎電影《春光乍洩》，都知道呢句說話嘅意思。海洋公園facebook噚日就出post，喺帖文話：「真的好想要你&hellip;&hellip;陪我來，#香港海洋公園，不只一下！」個post仲hashtag埋「#春光乍洩」，話趁呢個曖昧嘅季節，「來點港式浪漫，讓心意乍現」咁話。<br />\n<br />\n個post進一步向《春光》致敬，睇過《春光》都會記得黎耀輝（梁朝偉飾）同何寶榮（張國榮飾）打得火熱嘅一幕。海洋公園嘅post就有兩位疑似hehe嘅人喺天台擁抱，面向觀眾嗰位仲緊閉雙眼，睇起上嚟幾享受咁，相信係想向《春光》嘅黎耀輝同何寶榮致敬。<br />\n<br />\n呢個post啱啱出嗰陣，大家都思疑係唔係改圖，《蘋果》就問咗海洋公園，證實呢個post的確係佢哋出嘅，出咗1日都唔夠，已經有超過3.3K個likes，無論你撐唔撐呢個post，園方都算做到宣傳效果啦。<br />\n<br />\n睇民點睇<br />\n錢君：幾時有女女版。<br />\n公視台語台：放蕩！請問如何買門票呢？<br />\nKar Mei Wong：我唔知啲反同嘅弱智人士係點諗，佢哋去唔去都好，真心no one cares。<br />\nThor Chan：我唔歧視同性戀，不過可唔可以拍得有美感啲呢？而家似係山寨惡搞feel多。<br />\n許青：太棒了！一定要支持！這才是多元的世界。<br />\nMan Him Ng：很恐怖！同運入侵海洋公園！傳統家庭價值應該是，我要怎樣教小孩？<br />\nAlbert Law：海洋公園，都要抽同運水。海洋公園唔係一家大細去嗎？另類當然可以，人各有自由，但唔係咁，男男是否要趕走家庭客呢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59389748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59389748&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9D2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=e2dec4a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59389748&h=1990d8e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59389748</a>"},{"pid":"d5c039786fb250f2ef6c824ee9b003d29391f466","tid":1069903,"uid":38988,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"海洋公園啲公關食屎架？"},{"pid":"553634f17265d42027434736022380748b11983f","tid":1069903,"uid":224561,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"啲細路睇到然後問返佢地老母就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85c7cd941ba169731ae79aa2e2d582f29e988fc","tid":1069903,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"553634f17265d42027434736022380748b11983f","tid":1069903,"uid":224561,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"啲細路睇到然後問返佢地老母就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"老母：佢地好好朋友，所以去海洋公園玩，哈哈，今晚想食乜餸呀？"},{"pid":"ce3841314a1532f559c154648e5b05b3d1a1cd9c","tid":1069903,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;係咪一個女仔拍架段片？"},{"pid":"3baeb4845ad25cdb695680dd18efcbc2dc91b7c3","tid":1069903,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85c7c